  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "2. Season the bass fillets with salt and pepper.",
    "3. In a pan, melt the butter over medium heat.",
    "4. Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "5. Arrange the bass fillets on a baking sheet.",
    "6. Spread the garlic butter mixture evenly over each fillet.",
    "7. Sprinkle breadcrumbs and chopped parsley over the fish.",
    "8. Place a lemon slice on top of each fillet.",
    "9. Bake for 12-15 minutes, or until the fish is cooked through.",
    "10. Serve immediately and enjoy!"
